Before compiling CASPER the CCPN C api must be compiled. Follow these steps:

cd {svn_root}/main/trunk/external-libs/c/ccpnmr
python installCApi.py

The following environment variables must be set
PYTHONINCLUDES
PYTHONLIBS

PYTHONINCLUDES and PYTHONLIBS are set to point at the relevant python files.
E.g.
PYTHONINCLUDES=/usr/include/python2.5
PYTHONLIBS=/usr/lib/python2.5/config

To compile CASPER just:

cd {svn_root}/main/trunk/application/casper
ant
